# Paper Trading Execution

## Buy Logic
spend = cash * sizePct
tokensBought = spend / price

cash -= spend
tokenUnits += tokensBought

## Sell Logic
tokensSold = tokenUnits * sizePct
cash += tokensSold * price
tokenUnits -= tokensSold

## Metrics
Track:
- PnL
- equity curve
- number of trades
- drawdown (optional)
